          }
        },
        "slider_UXmznT": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "It really works!!",
            "text": "<p>“I used three time so far. I can see the results from first time I used. I love this product but only thing is it’s take time to apply till used all serum per application. I tried many different way to press to my skin so the serum come out more but then a lot of time not.”</p>",
